 A Salesforce Admin manages and maintains the Salesforce system.
 A Salesforce Developer builds custom features using code.
 Admin mostly works with settings and tools.
 Developer mostly works with programming languages.
 Admin creates users, reports, and dashboards.
 Developer creates custom apps and automation.
 Admin usually does not need coding knowledge.
 Developer uses Apex, Visualforce, and LWC coding.
 Admin improves daily business operations
 Developer adds advanced functionality based on company needs.
